  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "区间 DP 的两大核心模型",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "模型一：左右扩展型",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>特点</strong>：每次操作都是在当前连续区间的<strong>左边缘</strong>或<strong>右边缘</strong>增加/删除一个元素。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>状态转移思想</strong>：<code>大区间 [i, j]</code> 的答案，一定是从 <code>[i+1, j]</code>（左边缩进一位）或者 <code>[i, j-1]</code>（右边缩进一位）转移过来的。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>复杂度</strong>：通常为 $O(N^2)$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>相关题</strong>： <a href=\"/p/cf245h-queries-for-number-of-palindromes\" class=\"wikilink\">CF245H Queries for Number of Palindromes</a>，<a href=\"/p/2026icpc西安邀请赛-c-palindromic-and-balanced\" class=\"wikilink\">2026ICPC西安邀请赛 C Palindromic and Balanced</a>，<a href=\"/p/nk131111f-小苯的对称序列\" class=\"wikilink\">NK131111F 小苯的对称序列</a>（ $O(N^3)$ 的<strong>特殊枚举方式</strong> ）",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "模型二：区间拆分/合并型",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>特点</strong>：操作不是仅仅在边缘进行，而是可以将相邻的两个元素或两个小区间<strong>合并</strong>，或者将一个大区间<strong>劈开</strong>。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>状态转移思想</strong>：<code>大区间 [i, j]</code> 的答案，是把它从中间某个位置 <code>k</code> 劈成两半（<code>[i, k]</code> 和 <code>[k+1, j]</code>），把这两个小区间的答案合并起来，再加上这次合并的代价。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>公式化表示</strong>：<code>dp[i][j] = max/min( dp[i][k] + dp[k+1][j] + cost )</code>",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>复杂度</strong>：通常为 $O(N^3)$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>相关题</strong>：<a href=\"/p/p1880-[noi1995]-石子合并\" class=\"wikilink\">P1880 [NOI1995] 石子合并</a>，<a href=\"/p/cf607b-zuma\" class=\"wikilink\">CF607B Zuma</a>，<a href=\"/p/cf1132f-clear-the-string\" class=\"wikilink\">CF1132F Clear the String</a>",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
